Dont tell people your Dreams, Show them😃

Pageant Diaries💃MrsSouthAsiaWorld❣️
Hair & Makeup by lovely @arvyas11 

Thank you for providing this amazing platform
@rashmibedi_official 

#peagent #peageantgirl #fashionblogger #rampwalk #fashion #fashiongram #fashionphotography #gown #mrssouthasiaworld #crown #fashiondesigner #designerwear #prettylady #ramplife #fashionmodel #modellife #modelling #modelshoot #fashionshoot #fashionphotography #fashionmodel #fashioninspo #inspirationdaily #fashioninfluencer 
#hyderabad #warangal #banglore #rayalseema

Life is all about Experiences. I am sharing one such incredible experience I will cherish for Life, it was the moment I stepped into Lime light and started walking on Ramp, I realised I broke all my insecurities & norms that people set for me
They said you cant wear shorts you have got dark knees🤭you cant wear sleeveless 🫣Oh your dress is so revealing 😱and list goes on & onnnn…it doesnt matter what you wear how you wear it,there will always be a Judging face right infront of you to demean & put you down, key is to just take what you want and leave the rest , I realized it little late , better late than never, Just Remember end of the day its all about you being yourself ,flaunting your charisma gracefully and embracing the Amazing life you created for yourself , be proud of it every damn second

This Pageant journey has  inspired me in many ways, just looking at the contestants who came with their toddlers ,Mums handling them in backstage & rocking the stage has taught me a lot about this passion driven World ,if you really love doing something nothing can stop you ,and all my pageant sisters are living examples of that 💕Keep inspiring 
Thank you @rashmibedi_official for leading this platform, from making me learn how to walk to boosting my Confidence, you influence & inspire everyone around you … Keep Rocking , cant wait to meet you all soon and lit the stage 🤍
